Create new folder as git-server on any drive
open cmd from git-server--> type[ git init repo --bare ]
right click git-server folder and go to properties-sharing-share-everyone-read-write
create 2 more folder
test===open cmd from test type[ git clone "url of git-server till repo folder"] and add commit push files inside repo
test2==open cmd from test type[ git clone "url of git-server till repo folder"] and add commit push files inside repo

type git pull on test cmd
